name: PT 2. THE TEZ SUPREME TACO
description: SHORTLY AFTER ENTERING TEZO BELL FLACO HAD ALREADY PUSHED PAST TWO VERY ELDERLY WOMEN TAKING THEIR SWEET TIME TO ORDER. (at least 143 if you combine their ages). DAMN NEAR SPITTING IN THE CASHIERS FACE FLACO BLURTS OUT GIVE ME ONE TEZ SUPREME TACO! THE CASHIER PUZZLED AS TO WHY TF THIS S.O.B. JUST CAME RUNNING IN HERE LIKE THAT, RELUCTANTLY TAKES FLACOS ORDER. (ok sir just one, weird but ok). BEFORE THAT DELICIOUS TEZ SUPREME TACO COULD EVEN REACH THE COUNTER FLACO WAS SMASHING IT INTO HIS GRIMY LITTLE CLUTCH. NOW WITH THAT TEZ BAKING IN HIS BELLY FLACO STARES AT THE CASHIER. THE CASHIER NOW VERY IMPATIENT ASK IS THER ANYTHING MORE HE COULD HELP WITH? TO BE CONTINUED……….
